arguments.name: X
arguments.description: The numeric value at which to evaluate the distribution.

arguments.name: Deg_freedom
arguments.description: An integer indicating the number of degrees of freedom.

arguments.name: Tails
arguments.description: Specifies the number of distribution tails to return. If Tails = 1, TDIST returns the one-tailed distribution. If Tails = 2, TDIST returns the two-tailed distribution.
